Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.02,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Selty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.64,Default,Izaya,0,0,0,,Còn vui hơn mình mong đợi nữa.
